et Ross Gay, offers a fresh vision of Smith's masterpiece.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aPhotography / General.2bisacsh1 aGay, Ross, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSmith, W. Eugene, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStephenson, Sam, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTrachtenberg, Alan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311079732940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226827018423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226827018/original  a978-3-11-079732-9  University of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles